.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH chat 1  "chat "
.SH NAME
chat \- Start interactive terminal chat
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBchat\fR [\fB\-\-agent\fR] [\fB\-\-session\fR] [\fB\-\-message\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Start interactive terminal chat
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-agent\fR \fI<AGENT>\fR
Agent ID to use instead of the resolved default agent
.TP
\fB\-\-session\fR \fI<SESSION>\fR
Existing session ID to resume
.TP
\fB\-\-message\fR \fI<MESSAGE>\fR
Initial message to send immediately after startup
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
